Reuse Template Message Names Across Your WhatsApp Business Accounts

You can now use the same template name for multiple WhatsApp Business accounts (WABAs) under the same Marketing Cloud Engagement business unit.

Where: This change applies to Marketing Cloud Engagement Corporate and Enterprise editions with WhatsApp Business Messaging.

When: This change applies to templates created on or after July 12, 2024.

Salesforce Help: Personalize Your WhatsApp Template Messages in Marketing Cloud Engagement
title: Reuse WhatsApp Business Template Names Across Multiple Accounts
